651
00:48:21,916 --> 00:48:22,875
Well...

652
00:48:23,833 --> 00:48:26,291
It's nothing much.
I think I can work on my songs.

653
00:48:27,875 --> 00:48:31,791
-Why don't you seem happy?
-Of course, I am happy.

654
00:48:33,208 --> 00:48:34,666
I'm only worried about you.

655
00:48:36,416 --> 00:48:38,125
If I have to go back to Bangkok,

656
00:48:38,750 --> 00:48:39,833
