Or bring you with me?

658
00:48:41,958 --> 00:48:44,625
I can be with anyone.

659
00:48:45,208 --> 00:48:47,708
But you must hurry back, okay?

660
00:48:49,166 --> 00:48:51,500
Okay, I promise.

661
00:48:52,958 --> 00:48:53,875
Now, go to sleep.

662
00:48:57,541 --> 00:48:59,000
Close your eyes.

