675
00:51:12,750 --> 00:51:15,500
Be prepared at the end of this semester.

676
00:51:18,708 --> 00:51:19,583
Pa!

677
00:51:21,041 --> 00:51:22,583
I have told you.

678
00:51:24,500 --> 00:51:27,541
I'll take the athlete quotas

