00:52:44,125 --> 00:52:48,875
I have to go to work on my music
in Bangkok.

695
00:52:49,541 --> 00:52:52,791
If I leave Faifoo with you,
will it be okay?

696
00:52:52,875 --> 00:52:54,708
Musa will also help.

697
00:52:54,791 --> 00:52:56,458
Of course, I'll take care of her.

698
00:52:57,833 --> 00:52:59,541
-Thank you very much.
-Do you want some tea?

699
00:53:00,291 --> 00:53:01,416
Yes, please.

700
00:53:09,625 --> 00:53:10,666
Thank you.

701
00:53:21,166 --> 00:53:22,958
