759
00:57:47,000 --> 00:57:48,250
Hi.

760
00:57:49,375 --> 00:57:53,083
-My Mama wants to give this to you.
-Thank you.

761
00:57:53,166 --> 00:57:55,791
-Say thank you for me, okay?
-Okay.

762
00:57:57,708 --> 00:57:58,916
Is Fern here?

