00:58:27,416 --> 00:58:30,583
How about you? How are you?

769
00:58:31,666 --> 00:58:33,250
I miss you so much.

770
00:58:36,791 --> 00:58:39,041
Why didn't you tell me
when Dad was leaving?

771
00:58:39,625 --> 00:58:41,333
Where are you going?

772
00:58:42,000 --> 00:58:43,750
I'll go to see Dad.

773
00:58:44,625 --> 00:58:46,041
Be careful, dear.

774
00:58:46,708 --> 00:58:48,791
Sharif, let's go to see my Dad.

