00:58:55,000 --> 00:58:56,583
Hurry up, Sharif. We won't be in time.

776
00:59:04,750 --> 00:59:05,916
Hurry up.

777
00:59:14,166 --> 00:59:15,125
Uncle.

778
00:59:15,208 --> 00:59:16,750
-Uncle, hello.
