01:02:27,250 --> 01:02:28,791
have become.

803
01:03:03,125 --> 01:03:04,208
Are you leaving?

804
01:03:08,583 --> 01:03:09,541
Yes,

805
01:03:10,250 --> 01:03:12,000
everything seems to be in place.

806
01:03:15,541 --> 01:03:17,791
I have a dream to follow with my friends.

807
01:03:18,500 --> 01:03:20,208
We see where to go now.

808
01:03:25,000 --> 01:03:26,000
What a pity.

809
01:03:28,625 --> 01:03:29,583
Excuse me?

810
01:03:33,583 --> 01:03:35,000
Your eyes,

811
01:03:36,208 --> 01:03:37,125
they seem to change.

812
01:03:49,791 --> 01:03:50,750
Fern,

813
01:03:51,791 --> 01:03:53,750
I'll take you home today.

814
01:03:54,166 --> 01:03:57,416
